{"word":"G4367 - προστάσσω - prostássō - pros-tas'-so - Bid","slug":"G4367","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προστάσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>prostássō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>pros-tas'-so"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bid"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"- Original: <b><el>προστάσσω</el></b> <p />- Transliteration: <b>Prostasso</b> <p />- Phonetic: <b>pros-tas'-so</b> <p class=\"def\">- Definition: </p> <p class='li260'><b>1.</b> to assign or ascribe to, join to </p> <p class='li260'><b>2.</b> to enjoin, order, prescribe, command </p> <p class='li520'><b>a.</b> to appoint, to define </p> <p class=\"origin\"/>- Origin: from <a href=\"#/G4314\">G4314</a> and <a href=\"#/G5021\">G5021</a> <p />- TDNT entry: 08:37,1 <p />- Part(s) of speech: Verb <p />- Strong's: From <a href=\"#/G4314\">G4314</a> and <a href=\"#/G5021\">G5021</a>; to <i>arrange towards</i> that is (figuratively) <b><i>enjoin</i></b>: - bid command. "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1296\">G1296</a>, <a href=\"#/G1297\">G1297</a>, <a href=\"#/G1299\">G1299</a>, <a href=\"#/G2004\">G2004</a>, <a href=\"#/G392\">G392</a>, <a href=\"#/G5001\">G5001</a>, <a href=\"#/G5021\">G5021</a>, <a href=\"#/G506\">G506</a>, <a href=\"#/G5292\">G5292</a>, <a href=\"#/G5293\">G5293</a>, <a href=\"#/G657\">G657</a>, <a href=\"#/G812\">G812</a>, <a href=\"#/G813\">G813</a>, <a href=\"#/G814\">G814</a>"}]}